727608f-a.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 84th Street
727608f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, east of 84th Street, showing
two views of Mrs. Booat's house of 1873. F. Joseph was the owner
in 1891.
May 1923
View 21  March 1924.
Nugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
